#### <a id='2f7d85b06c1adab1d8e2f2ce3999ead2'></a>market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.total.${code}.metrics.rps

[Preview query:](https://yql.yandex-team.ru/?query_type=CLICKHOUSE&query=use%20marketclickhouse%3B%0A%0ASELECT%0A%20%20%20%20multiply(intDiv(timestamp%2C%2060)%2C%2060)%20AS%20metric_ts%2C%0A%20%20%20%20count()%20%2F%2060%20as%20value_0%2C%0A%20%20%20%20service_black%2C%0A%20%20%20%20code%0A%0AFROM%20market.nginx2%0A%0AWHERE%20date%20%3D%20today()%20and%20timestamp%20%3E%20now()%20-%2060%20*%2060%0A%20%20%20%20AND%20(environment%20%3D%20'PRODUCTION'%20and%20url%20!%3D%20'%2Fping'%20and%20service_black%20!%3D%20'undefined_service')%0A%0AGROUP%20BY%20metric_ts%2C%0A%20%20%20%20multiIf(%20vhost%20%3D%20'business.market.yandex.ru'%2C%20'black_desktop'%20%2C%20'undefined_service'%20)%20as%20service_black%2C%0A%20%20%20%20arrayJoin(%5B'any-code'%2C%20concat(substring(toString(http_code)%2C1%2C1)%2C'xx')%2C%20toString(http_code)%5D)%20as%20code%0A%0AORDER%20BY%20metric_ts%20LIMIT%2010)
```SQL
SELECT
    multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
    count() / 60 as value_0,
    service_black,
    code

FROM market.nginx2

WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60
    AND (environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service')

GROUP BY metric_ts,
    multiIf( vhost = 'business.market.yandex.ru', 'black_desktop' , 'undefined_service' ) as service_black,
    arrayJoin(['any-code', concat(substring(toString(http_code),1,1),'xx'), toString(http_code)]) as code

ORDER BY metric_ts LIMIT 10
```

```SQL
SELECT 
    'market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.total.${code}.metrics.rps' AS title, 
    count() AS cnt
     
FROM (
    SELECT
        multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
        count() / 60 as value_0,
        service_black,
        code
    
    FROM market.nginx2
    
    WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60
        AND (environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service')
    
    GROUP BY metric_ts,
        multiIf( vhost = 'business.market.yandex.ru', 'black_desktop' , 'undefined_service' ) as service_black,
        arrayJoin(['any-code', concat(substring(toString(http_code),1,1),'xx'), toString(http_code)]) as code
)

GROUP BY metric_ts
ORDER BY cnt DESC
LIMIT 1
```

SELECT 
    'market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.robot.splits.${robot}.${code}.metrics.rps' AS title, 
    count() AS cnt
     
FROM (

    count() / 60 as value_0,

SELECT 
    'market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.robot.resolver.splits.${robot}.${resolver}.${code}.metrics.rps' AS title, 
    count() AS cnt
     
FROM (
    SELECT
        multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
        count() / 60 as value_0,
        service_black,
        robot,
        resolver,
        code
    
    FROM market.nginx2
    
    WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60
        AND (environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service' and robot != '' and page_id in ('api:resolve', 'fapi:api'))
    
    GROUP BY metric_ts,
        multiIf( vhost = 'business.market.yandex.ru', 'black_desktop' , 'undefined_service' ) as service_black,
        replaceRegexpAll(extract(user_agent,'Googlebot|GoogleDocs|Google-Ads-Creatives-Assistant|YaDirectBot|YaDirectFetcher|YandexRCA|YandexDirectDyn|YandexAccessibilityBot|Mail.RU_Bot|BingPreview|Mediapartners-Google|Feedfetcher-Google;|AdsBot-Google|Yahoo! Slurp|WebAlta|StackRambler|msnbot|bingbot|Aport|Mail\\.Ru/|Yandex/|Statbox/|YandexSomething/|YandexBlog/|Yandex\\.Server/|YaDirectBot|Jakarta Commons-HttpClient/|TurtleScanner|Novoteka|ia_archiver|heritrix|Twiceler-|psbot/|Alchemy Eye Agent|Echoping/|Friends/|WhatsUp/|WhatsUp_Gold/|; HttpSatPinger\\)|MSRBOT \\(http://research\\.microsoft\\.com/research/sv/msrbot/|MJ12bot/|ichiro/|TECOMAC-Crawler/|Gigabot|Sogou Push Spider|check_http/|http_ping|KeepAliveClient|SamSunf|GenHash|IRLbot|UptimeInspector|liveinternet spider|Begun Robot Crawler|InternetSeer\\.com|Refer\\.Ru Favicon Bot|Robot Semonitor|Robot PagePromoter|SESpider|Jakarta Commons-HttpClient|Parasite Eliminator|Spinn3r|YandexBot/|YandexImages/|YandexVideo/|YandexMedia/|YandexBlogs/|YandexFavicons/|YandexAddurl/|YandexImageResizer/|YandexDirect/|YandexMetrika/|YandexNews/|YandexCatalog/|YandexWebmaster/'),'[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '') as robot,
        replaceRegexpAll(decodeURLComponent(arrayJoin(multiIf(page_id = 'api:resolve', arrayFilter(x -> x != '', arrayMap(x -> if(splitByChar('=', x)[1] = 'r', splitByChar('=', x)[2], ''), extractURLParameters(url))), page_id = 'fapi:api', [extractURLParameter(url, 'name')], ['unknown']))),'[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '_') as resolver,
        arrayJoin(['any-code', concat(substring(toString(http_code),1,1),'xx'), toString(http_code)]) as code

    'market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.resourceType.splits.${resource-type}.${code}.metrics.ttlb.quantiles' AS title, 
    count() AS cnt

    SELECT
        multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
        quantilesTimingIf(0.5,0.6,0.7,0.80,0.90,0.95,0.97,0.99,0.995,0.997,0.999,1)(resptime_ms,environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service') as value_0,
        service_black,

        code

    WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60
        AND (environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service')

        multiIf( vhost = 'business.market.yandex.ru', 'black_desktop' , 'undefined_service' ) as service_black,

SELECT 
    'market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.dc.resolver.splits.${dc}.${resolver}.${code}.metrics.req_time.quantiles' AS title, 
    count() AS cnt
     
FROM (
    SELECT
        multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
        quantilesTimingIf(0.5,0.6,0.7,0.80,0.90,0.95,0.97,0.99,0.995,0.997,0.999,1)(client_reqtime_ms,environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service' and page_id in ('api:resolve', 'fapi:api')) as value_0,

        dc,
        resolver,
        code

    WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60
        AND (environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service' and page_id in ('api:resolve', 'fapi:api'))
    
    GROUP BY metric_ts,
        multiIf( vhost = 'business.market.yandex.ru', 'black_desktop' , 'undefined_service' ) as service_black,
        multiIf( substring(host, 1, 3) in ('iva', 'man', 'vla', 'sas', 'myt'), substring(host, 1, 3), endsWith(host, 'yp-c.yandex.net'), substring(host, position(host, '.') + 1, 3), dictGetString('dc', 'dc', sipHash64(host)) <> '', dictGetString('dc', 'dc', sipHash64(host)), 'undefined_dc' ) as dc,

)

GROUP BY metric_ts
ORDER BY cnt DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
    'market-front-unified.nginx2.v2.${service_black}.requester.resourceType.splits.${requester}.${resource-type}.${code}.metrics.bytes_send.quantiles' AS title,

SELECT
    multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
    quantilesIf(0.5,0.7,0.9,0.95,0.97,0.99,0.995,1)(bytes_sent,environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service' and robot != '') as value_0,

WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60

1)%2C'xx')%2C%20toString(http_code)%5D)%20as%20code%0A%0AORDER%20BY%20metric_ts%20LIMIT%2010)
```SQL
SELECT
    multiply(intDiv(timestamp, 60), 60) AS metric_ts,
    quantilesIf(0.5,0.7,0.9,0.95,0.97,0.99,0.995,1)(bytes_sent,environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service' and page_id in ('api:resolve', 'fapi:api')) as value_0,
    service_black,
    dc,
    resolver,
    code

FROM market.nginx2

WHERE date = today() and timestamp > now() - 60 * 60
    AND (environment = 'PRODUCTION' and url != '/ping' and service_black != 'undefined_service' and page_id in ('api:resolve', 'fapi:api'))

GROUP BY metric_ts,
    multiIf( vhost = 'business.market.yandex.ru', 'black_desktop' , 'undefined_service' ) as service_black,
    multiIf( substring(host, 1, 3) in ('iva', 'man', 'vla', 'sas', 'myt'), substring(host, 1, 3), endsWith(host, 'yp-c.yandex.net'), substring(host, position(host, '.') + 1, 3), dictGetString('dc', 'dc', sipHash64(host)) <> '', dictGetString('dc', 'dc', sipHash64(host)), 'undefined_dc' ) as dc,
    replaceRegexpAll(decodeURLComponent(arrayJoin(multiIf(page_id = 'api:resolve', arrayFilter(x -> x != '', arrayMap(x -> if(splitByChar('=', x)[1] = 'r', splitByChar('=', x)[2], ''), extractURLParameters(url))), page_id = 'fapi:api', [extractURLParameter(url, 'name')], ['unknown']))),'[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '_') as resolver,
    arrayJoin(['any-code', concat(substring(toString(http_code),1,1),'xx'), toString(http_code)]) as code

ORDER BY metric_ts LIMIT 10
```

GROUP BY metric_ts
